Object.Field: LKM File to Sybase IQ (LOAD TABLE)

Author: Sunopsis Version: 4.0 Last Update: Jul-2006
Description: - Loading Knowledge Module - Bulk Loads data from a flat file into Sybase AS IQ using the LOAD TABLE command. - This module sends a LOAD TABLE command to the Sybase IQ database so that the database will use the loading utility to load files.
Restrictions: - This Knowledge Module assumes that the file being loaded is on the same box as the Sybase AS IQ server.
Latest Changes: - The information about the column delimiter, the row seperator, and the number of skipped header rows are being taken from the model.
Set this option to NO if you wish to retain temporary objects (tables, files and scripts) after integration. Useful for debugging.
The maximum amount of memory (in MB) that Sybase IQ will use to load the file.

create table <%=snpRef.getTable("L", "COLL_NAME", "A")%> ( <%=snpRef.getColList("", "[CX_COL_NAME]\t[DEST_WRI_DT] " + snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL"), ",\n\t", "","")%> <% if (snpRef.getSrcTablesList("", "[FILE_FORMAT]", "", "").equals("F")) {%>, SNP_PAD VARCHAR(100)<%}%> )

<% if ("C".equals(snpRef.getJrnInfo( "JRN_METHOD"))) { %> /* Consistant journalization detected. */ /* Lock should be done by a specific step in a package */ <% } else { %> update <%=snpRef.getTable( "L" , "JRN_NAME" , "A" )%> set JRN_CONSUMED = '1' where (1=1) <%=snpRef.getJrnFilter()%> <% } %>

<% if (snpRef.getSrcTablesList("", "[FILE_FORMAT]", "", "").equals("D")) {%> LOAD TABLE <%=snpRef.getTable("L", "COLL_NAME", "A")%> ( <%=snpRef.getColList("", "[CX_COL_NAME]", ",\n\t", "","")%> ) FROM '<%=snpRef.getSrcTablesList("", "[SCHEMA]/[RES_NAME]", "","")%>' QUOTES OFF ESCAPES OFF FORMAT ascii DELIMITED BY '\x<%=snpRef.getSrcTablesList("", "[FILE_SEP_FIELD]", "", "")%>' ROW DELIMITED BY '\x<%=snpRef.getSrcTablesList("", "[FILE_SEP_ROW]", "", "")%>' SKIP <%=snpRef.getSrcTablesList("", "[FILE_FIRST_ROW]", "", "")%>
<%} else {%> LOAD TABLE <%=snpRef.getTable("L", "COLL_NAME", "W")%> ( <%=snpRef.getColList("", "[CX_COL_NAME] ASCII([BYTES])", ",\n\t", "","")%> ) FROM '<%=snpRef.getSrcTablesList("", "[SCHEMA]/[RES_NAME]", "","")%>' QUOTES OFF ESCAPES OFF FORMAT ascii ROW DELIMITED BY '\x<%=snpRef.getSrcTablesList("", "[FILE_SEP_ROW]", "", "")%>' SKIP <%=snpRef.getSrcTablesList("", "[FILE_FIRST_ROW]", "", "")%> <% } %>

<% if ("C".equals(snpRef.getJrnInfo( "JRN_METHOD"))) { %> /* Consistant journalization detected. */ /* Lock should be done by a specific step in a package */ <% } else { %> delete from <%=snpRef.getTable("L","JRN_NAME","A")%> where JRN_CONSUMED = '1' <%=snpRef.getJrnFilter()%> <% } %>
